<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<%- include('partials/head', { pageTitle, siteName: brand.name, brand }) %>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header', { brand }) %>

<style>
.ls-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0a00 0%, #2d1200 50%, #1a0a00 100%);
  padding: 3rem 1rem 2.5rem;
  text-align: center;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #ff7a1a33;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.ls-hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #ff7a1a18 0%, transparent 70%);
}
.ls-hero .eyebrow {
  font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .18em; color: #ff7a1a;
  text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: .6rem;
}
.ls-hero h1 {
  font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff;
  line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: .8rem; position: relative;
}
.ls-hero h1 span { color: #ff7a1a; }
.ls-hero p {
  color: #bbb; font-size: .9rem; max-width: 480px;
  margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; position: relative;
}
.ls-back {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem;
  color: #ff7a1a; font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
}
.ls-back:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
.era-tabs {
  display: flex; gap: .5rem; justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 1.5rem 1rem 0;
  background: #fff8f3;
}
.era-btn {
  padding: .4rem 1rem; border-radius: 99px;
  border: 1.5px solid #e0d0c0; background: #fff;
  color: #666; cursor: pointer; font-size: .78rem;
  font-weight: 600; transition: all .2s; font-family: inherit;
}
.era-btn.active, .era-btn:hover {
  background: #ff7a1a; border-color: #ff7a1a; color: #fff;
}
.ls-container {
  max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
  background: #fff8f3;
}
.roadmap { position: relative; padding: 0 0 2rem; }
.roadmap::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, #ff7a1a 5%, #ff7a1a 95%, transparent 100%);
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
.rm-item {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem; position: relative;
  transition: opacity .3s;
}
.rm-item.hidden { display: none; }
.rm-item:nth-child(odd)  { flex-direction: row; }
.rm-item:nth-child(even) { flex-direction: row-reverse; }
.rm-card {
  width: calc(50% - 2.5rem);
  background: #fff; border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1.5px solid #f0e0d0;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px #ff7a1a0a;
  transition: all .25s;
}
.rm-card:hover {
  border-color: #ff7a1a;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 24px #ff7a1a18;
  transform: translateY(-3px);
}
.rm-img {
  width: 100%; height: 130px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe8d0, #ffd0a8);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 2.8rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.rm-img::after {
  content: 'Ảnh sẽ cập nhật';
  position: absolute; bottom: 6px; right: 8px;
  font-size: .6rem; color: #ff7a1a88; font-style: italic;
}
.rm-body { padding: .9rem 1rem; }
.rm-era-tag {
  font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: #ff7a1a;
  background: #fff3ea; padding: .2rem .6rem;
  border-radius: 99px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: .4rem;
}
.rm-year { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: .15rem; }
.rm-title { font-size: .92rem; font-weight: 700; color: #333; margin-bottom: .4rem; line-height: 1.3; }
.rm-desc { font-size: .78rem; color: #777; line-height: 1.5; }
.rm-dot {
  position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 1.5rem;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: #ff7a1a; border: 4px solid #fff8f3;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #ff7a1a;
  z-index: 2; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.era-divider {
  text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
}
.era-divider span {
  background: #ff7a1a; color: #fff;
  font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; padding: .4rem 1.2rem;
  border-radius: 99px; display: inline-block;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .roadmap::before { left: 1.2rem; }
  .rm-item,
  .rm-item:nth-child(even) { flex-direction: column !important; padding-left: 3rem; }
  .rm-card { width: 100%; }
  .rm-dot { left: 1.2rem; top: .8rem; }
  .rm-img { height: 100px; }
}
.back-top {
  display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;
  color: #ff7a1a; font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none; padding: .8rem;
}
.back-top:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>

<div class="ls-hero">
  <a href="/" class="ls-back">← Về trang chủ</a>
  <p class="eyebrow">Trạm Sử Meta</p>
  <h1>Lược sử <span>Việt Nam</span></h1>
  <p>Hành trình 4.000 năm dựng nước và giữ nước — từ Kinh Dương Vương đến ngày nay</p>
</div>

<div class="era-tabs">
  <button class="era-btn active" onclick="filterEra('all', this)">Tất cả</button>
  <button class="era-btn" onclick="filterEra('dung-nuoc', this)">Dựng nước</button>
  <button class="era-btn" onclick="filterEra('bac-thuoc', this)">Bắc thuộc</button>
  <button class="era-btn" onclick="filterEra('doc-lap', this)">Độc lập</button>
  <button class="era-btn" onclick="filterEra('can-hien-dai', this)">Cận – Hiện đại</button>
</div>

<div class="ls-container">
